timelineItems.title: GOAL: Vicente Sanchez opens the scoring early against Vancouver

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: In theory, I should be afraid of a Doyle/Sanchez partnership up top. Based on their performance to date, though, I'm not. #COLvVAN #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Sal Cipriano
timelineItems.text: Meh, not a handball. Gotta protect your privates. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Julian Dierkes
timelineItems.text: Flores running to make Colorado's head spin. #TrustInRobbo #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Victor Sum
timelineItems.text: Colorado's coach shaved off his epic mustache!! He no longer looks like a super villain 😞 #VWFC #COLvsVAN

timelineItems.name: Walter Siu
timelineItems.text: The problem with playing both Koffie and Flores at the same time: they both like to move up the field. Going to be a long match. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Julian Dierkes
timelineItems.text: "Mattocks lays it off beautifully" Clearly Mattocks 2015, not 2014. Maybe he will score... #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Radio Cascadia
timelineItems.text: Kekuta Manneh never ceases to impress me. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Attempt blocked. Marcelo Sarvas (Colorado Rapids) right footed shot from outside the box is blocked.
timelineItems.title: SAVE: David Ousted's quick palm denies Luis Solignac

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Well, at least they're getting chances. Need to work the ball better. Robbo also needs to stop working the 4th ref. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Give the man Save of the Week, Save of the Year and Goalkeeper of the Year. What more does he have to do? #COLvVAN #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Radio Cascadia
timelineItems.text: GREAT save by Ousted! #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Paul S-H
timelineItems.text: Is Ousted real?!? Or is he made of pixie dust and magic?!? #vwfc

timelineItems.desc: Goal!  Colorado Rapids 1, Vancouver Whitecaps FC 1. Kekuta Manneh (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) left footed shot from the left side of the six yard box.

timelineItems.name: Sal Cipriano
timelineItems.text: Ousted is the goalie of the year. Everyone else should just stop playing and let their backups do the job. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.desc: The Vancouver Whitecaps take their three-game road winning streak to Dick’s Sporting Goods Park where they face the struggling Colorado Rapids.

timelineItems.text: HT: Rapids 1- Whitecaps 1. After a horrendous start, Vancouver were able to level the match and have had the better game so far. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Julian Dierkes
timelineItems.text: Really fun half to watch (except for stupid goal). Koffie-Flores not a revelation. @PeteSchaad "Ousted to the rescue" #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Michael Chambers
timelineItems.text: Colorado's set pieces are making me nervous. #WhitecapsFC not exactly defending them flawlessly. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: An even score to start the 2nd half may be part of Robbo's plan. Laba off the bench to guard a result is a luxury few dream of. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Beita looked very good on that track-back. Much better game for him tonight so far. Rough road trip for Beita. #COLvVAN #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Mun Bagri
timelineItems.text: I think once Mezquida comes in for Rosales at 60 mins, he'll really start to push their transition game that much quicker. #SpeedKills #VWFC
